data.description: Charming cabin on 20 acres bordering Forest Service offers no restrictive covenants w/the convenience of fiber optic internet, so you can enjoy the best of both worlds while working from home. This 2 bd, office and 1-1/2 bath home boasts a spacious, partially-covered deck, allowing you to relish the mountain views as the wildlife frequents the property. Inside, enjoy the wood-clad sun room throughout the day or the living room adorned with large windows which bathes the space in natural light, creating an atmosphere of serenity. You have 1bd on the main floor w/half ba while the upstairs hosts a lg bd, lg closet with full bath. Basement offers an office & an open area that could be used for crafting w stairs to outside. Lg 2 car garage w/room above. RV hookup. Partially fenced for horses. House is wired to run a generator and propane lighting is already in place. Seasonal spring and views puts the finishing touches on this property. Listed by Leslie Reeder
